Class PhysicsObject

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.pcc.pams.objects.PhysicsObject
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Bubble, Fan, Wall

    class PhysicsObject
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents a 2D object that has a position and a speed.
